OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781115079
OL,3,CWoman calling for better mental health
OL,4,Csupport for care leavers
OL,6,FShe said: "If I'm really honest, it's
OL,7,Flucky I'm still here because it could
OL,8,Fhave been a very different story.
OL,10,F"I turned to drink, I was on this
OL,11,Fcouncil estate I was going to parties,
OL,12,FI had an ASBO (Anti-Social Behaviour
OL,13,FOrder) before I was 18. I was in debt
OL,14,Fwhen I was 19, I got blacklisted at 20.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781115079
OL,3,CWoman calling for better mental health
OL,4,Csupport for care leavers
OL,6,F"I used to drink and do drugs with my
OL,7,Fmedicine, I was getting arrested every
OL,8,Fweekend. I was a young girl, but
OL,9,Finstead of people asking 'why is this
OL,10,Fyoung girl in the stalls again', it
OL,11,Fwas petty stuff, nobody picked up on
OL,12,Fthe life that I'd come from."
OL,14,FGemma now works as a mental health
OL,15,Fempowerment mentor with 60 others
OL,16,Facross the UK, as well as leading
OL,17,F'Inspired Empowerment'- a charity
OL,18,Fsupporting young people through
OL,19,Fmentoring and early intervention, and
OL,20,Fteaching them life skills.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781115079
OL,3,CWoman calling for better mental health
OL,4,Csupport for care leavers
OL,6,FShe said: "All my life I've struggled
OL,7,Fwith my mental health, I've struggled
OL,8,Fwith relationships, I have the fear of
OL,9,Fabandonment all the time so as soon as
OL,10,Fanyone got close to me i'd push them
OL,11,Faway."
OL,13,FGemma said many care leavers are not
OL,14,Fgiven life tools or taught how to live
OL,15,Findependently.
OL,17,FShe said: "I feel like every child in
OL,18,Fthe care system, they're our most
OL,19,Fvulnerable children, why should they
OL,20,Fnot be given a trauma informed mentor?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781115079
OL,3,CWoman calling for better mental health
OL,4,Csupport for care leavers
OL,6,F"Someone to help them unpack all the
OL,7,Fstuff that's going on in their mind,
OL,8,Fbecause believe me, my mind never
OL,9,Fswitched off."
OL,11,FGemma said that while a lot of money
OL,12,Fis invested in prisons, hospitals,
OL,13,Fhomelessness and crime, it may be more
OL,14,Fbeneficial to "reach people when
OL,15,Fthey're young".
OL,17,FFor her campaign to reach parliament,
OL,18,FGemma's petition needs 10,000
OL,19,Fsignatures by October.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1781115079
OL,3,CWoman calling for better mental health
OL,4,Csupport for care leavers
OL,6,FShe said: "You can do and be anything
OL,7,Fyou want to be and give them that
OL,8,Fbelief. Let them write their own
OL,9,Fstories, they deserve that."
OL,11,FThe Department for Education have been
OL,12,Fcontacted for comment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
